back from El Ourdoun
2007/05/05 토요일 오전 3:23:48
Hello Kim
I'm sorry that it took me more than one month to send you the pictures...
I hope your trip in Middle East was great and that you're safe back in Korea.
I spent only one week in Jordan before going back to Abu Dhabi, but it was an unforgettable week. We saw beautiful places and met amazingly nice people, especially the bedouins in Petra and Wadi Rum. I ate the good chocolates you kindly offered to me with bedouin kids !
Some pictures here attached.
coming back in UAE was really difficult after Jordan. I miss the nature and simplicity of people, being able to walk outside without stopping every two minutes for the cars, and without breathing exhaust fumes !!
If you write to me I would enjoy reading about your trip in Syria and around.
all the best for your future, in Korea or elsewhere !
Delphine
